### Hadith 3:274

*Narrated Jabir:*

While we were offering the prayer with the Prophet a caravan carrying
food came from Sham. The people looked towards the caravan (and went to
it) and only twelve persons remained with the Prophet. So, the Divine
Inspiration came; "But when they see some bargain or some amusement,
they disperse headlong to it." (62.11)

